      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a lovely finish with only minor surface scratches and a few tiny stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing light wear on the driver's seat bolster but otherwise in great shape. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should.",
