    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "For sale is a vehicle in poor condition. The engine requires major repairs and is currently not running reliably. The exterior has significant rust and body damage, and the interior shows heavy wear and staining. This car is being sold as-is for parts or a complete restoration project.",
