    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a slightly aged suspension feel over bumps. Cosmestically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind doing a bit of preventative maintenance down the road.",
