    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and has been loved, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
