    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis has been meticulously prepared, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and an overhauled dual-VANOS system to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Suspension dynamics are enhanced by Bilstein PSS10 adjustable coilovers, while the factory Style 67 wheels are wrapped in new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires for maximum lateral grip. Every mechanical component, from the limited-slip differential to the rod bearings, has been serviced or replaced to meet exacting standards. The exterior finish and Nappa leather interior remain in showroom condition, free of any cosmetic or structural imperfections.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
